{"type": "article", "id": 22254, "title": "三宅一生和Littala的合作系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-15T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 84, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150116ivpaNeb5sdBWCm9T.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是日本设计师三宅一生和芬兰家居品牌 Iittala 推出的 2016 年新品，有 30 种产品，包括陶瓷杯、玻璃杯和纺织品。其中一款陶瓷杯是五边形的，对应的杯碟和杯垫也是五边形，而杯垫更采用了折叠的方式，层层叠加而有了立体效果，像是花朵绽放的瞬间。这套餐具名为“日常仪式”，给日常用品更多细致。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061501146PHozDcpOStJ79kZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150115wiqrheo4PtFzWCZY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150115BP4QsZpqnVCuO86o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66259169\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150115wH2rg3RTBzW5LYVu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09046455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}